## 🎯 Project Overview

This repository contains RTL design, verification and synthesis flows for a MIPS-like CPU study project.

The project focuses on:

- **Single-cycle CPU** (`source/design/single_cycle/`): complete processor datapath and control.

### What is included

✅ Verilog/SystemVerilog design source files  
✅ Verification testbenches and assembly test programs  
✅ Simulation scripts for Icarus Verilog  
✅ Generic synthesis flow (technology-independent)  
✅ Sky130-specific synthesis flow (technology mapping)  
✅ Environment setup and validation scripts (`setup.sh`, `synth/check_env.sh`)  

---

## 📁 Repository Structure

```text
single-cycle/
├── README
├── setup.sh                         # Local environment bootstrap (.env creation)
├── .env.example                     # Configuration template
├── .env                             # Local environment configuration (generated)
├── simu/
│   ├── simulate.sh                  # Simulation script
│   └── *.vcd                        # Generated waveform files
├── source/
│   ├── design/
│   │   └── single_cycle/
│   │       ├── alu.v
│   │       ├── control_unit.v
│   │       ├── cpu.v
│   │       ├── data_mem.v
│   │       ├── instr_mem.v
│   │       └── register_file_.v
│   └── verif/
│       ├── alu_test.sv
│       ├── control_unit_test.sv
│       ├── cpu_test.sv
│       ├── data_mem_test.sv
│       ├── instr_mem_test.sv
│       ├── register_file_test.sv
│       └── assembly/
│           ├── andi.hex
│           ├── basic_swlw.hex
│           ├── beq.hex
│           ├── blt.hex
│           ├── bne.hex
│           ├── border_swlw.hex
│           ├── fibonacci.hex
│           ├── fibonacci_overflow.hex
│           ├── integration.hex
│           ├── jump.hex
│           ├── lui.hex
│           ├── ori.hex
│           ├── regs.hex
│           ├── rtype.hex
│           ├── sll.hex
│           └── srl.hex
└── synth/
    ├── config.sh                    # Loads .env / env vars and validates paths
    ├── check_env.sh                 # Environment health check
    ├── generic_synth.sh             # Generic synthesis script
    ├── specific_synth.sh            # Sky130 mapping synthesis script
    ├── *_generic_synth.v            # Generated generic synthesis netlists
    ├── *_specific_synth.v           # Generated Sky130 synthesis netlists
    ├── *.json                       # Generated JSON netlists
    └── *.svg                        # Generated netlist diagrams (if netlistsvg available)
```

