## 📌 Important Commands

### Setup

| Command               |                      Purpose                        |
|-----------------------|-----------------------------------------------------|
| `./setup.sh`          | Create/update local `.env` and validate environment |
| `synth/check_env.sh`  | Run environment health check                        |

### Simulation

| Command                                 | Purpose                |
|-----------------------------------------|------------------------|
| `cd simu && ./simulate.sh cpu`          | Run CPU simulation     |
| `cd simu && ./simulate.sh cpu +test=N`  | Run specific CPU test  |

### Synthesis

| Command                                     | Purpose                                |
|---------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------|
| `cd synth && ./generic_synth.sh <module>`   | Generic synthesis                      |
| `cd synth && ./specific_synth.sh <module>`  | Sky130 technology mapping              |

### Debug/inspection

| Command                                                        | Purpose              |
|----------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------|
| `gtkwave simu/cpu.vcd`                                     | Open waveform        |
| `find ~ -name "*sky130_fd_sc_hd*tt_100C_1v80.lib" 2>/dev/null` | Locate Sky130 liberty|

